      <p>Clean Arcade is a collection of free browser games. No ads, no tracking, no accounts. Every game runs directly in your browser — nothing to download or sign up for. Game progress and favorites are saved locally and never leave your device. Most games work on mobile. Available in 100+ languages.</p>
      <p>We don't collect your data. All saves, favorites, and preferences stay in your browser's localStorage. Nothing is sent to any server. Third-party services: <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cloudflare Pages</a> (hosting), <a href="https://bunny.net/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Bunny Fonts</a> (web fonts), <a href="https://gtranslate.io/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GTranslate</a> (translation).</p>
      <p>To clear locally stored data: Developer Tools &rarr; Application &rarr; Local Storage &rarr; delete entries for this domain.</p>
